# Dashboard Structure

The dashboard is the main application interface after login, organized into several sections.

## Main Layout

- [app/[locale]/dashboard/layout.tsx](mdc:app/[locale]/dashboard/layout.tsx): Dashboard layout with navigation
- [app/[locale]/dashboard/page.tsx](mdc:app/[locale]/dashboard/page.tsx): Dashboard homepage

## Sections

The dashboard is organized into these primary sections:

### CRM

- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/crm/contacts`: Contact management
- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/crm/company`: Company management
- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/crm/team`: Team management

### Workspace

- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/workspace/tasks`: Task management
- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/workspace/calendar`: Calendar view

### Resources

- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/resource/content`: Content management
- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/resource/emails`: Email templates

### Site Management

- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/site/(general)/management`: Site management
- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/site/(admin)`: Admin controls

### Account

- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/account/settings`: User settings
- `/app/[locale]/dashboard/account/notifications`: Notification settings
